cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about a framework for distributed reinforcement learning, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence (AI) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The framework also involves distributed computing, which could fall under categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper mentions specific reinforcement learning algorithms, which could also place it in the cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) category.
